    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is being sold as-is. While it remains operational and starts consistently, the engine shows signs of age and the transmission, though functional, isn't as crisp as it once was. There are noticeable cosmetic imperfections, including some interior wear and minor exterior dings. It serves as a reliable budget option for someone willing to put in a little work or looking for a daily driver that doesn't need to be perfect.",
